close_reason: "Shipped the describe verb's render leg: new SDK primitive renderExtensionSurfaceMarkdown(summary, options?) (src/core/extensions/activation-summary-markdown.ts, re-exported from the SDK barrel) renders any ExtensionActivationSummary to a deterministic Markdown reference doc; pm extension/package describe --markdown composes per-extension + union sections (renderExtensionDescribeMarkdown in describe.ts) via the dispatch in register-setup.ts (fails fast: --markdown requires the describe action and conflicts with --json). Contracts (EXTENSION_FLAG_CONTRACTS + EXTENSION_DESCRIBE_FLAG_CONTRACTS + COMMAND_ARG_CONTRACTS describe/lifecycle, full.json regenerated), completion (bash auto via contracts, zsh+fish manual), and docs (SDK.md + EXTENSIONS.md) updated. 100/100/100/100 coverage on all three touched modules; full suite 5122 tests green; static/docs-skills/docs-links/contracts gates green."
